/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從來少數都要妥協多數<br />\n兩邊唔妥協咪搞大佢囉<br />\n黑色旅遊警示  宵禁囉<br />\n大家根本無所謂 攬炒囉<br />\n<br />\n有權有勢有錢嘅只會諗自己利益<br />\n唔想經濟下滑樓價暴跌<br />\n咁呢31005人好快會變condom<br />\n睇下邊個成為最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7e3d47cabb80303656f40d449388b112edf6d5","tid":1355641,"uid":268540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"有frd住大埔，聽說好似好憎警察"},{"pid":"77d893441d2bd466d1de296a9ba9819a9f5f8bae","tid":1355641,"uid":192749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:15:13.000Z","msg":"拉老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢找左條尾先先出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n血汗錢 人地做野咁辛苦都唔肯出<br />\n點幫佢做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0361f0c462c330abe1a7518ba9a1320248ad60ae","tid":1355641,"uid":264624,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:16:43.000Z","msg":"而家梗係乜都唔做食花生睇好戲<br />\n等佢哋自己打生打死<br />\n去嚟做乜尻"},{"pid":"c15f61cea4be09cda17b795f5e13acb2d83f6837","tid":1355641,"uid":87326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"113c5c308f799d3d2c06dcd2e5f344751c0707f5","tid":1355641,"uid":24477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T10:46:58.000Z","msg":"大埔group有人話佢會出席鄉事委員會飯局<br />\n如果佢真係去 連祖宗山墳都唔理<br />\n好大機會借呢單野拉攏其他牛屎佬<br />\n純粹個人意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:18:25.000Z","msg":"佢去完個山墳理左啦喎<br />\n咁係咪完啦呢個post"},{"pid":"fc214ae772b67c31567f06528faa9e2a87285180","tid":1355641,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:19:51.000Z","msg":"唔知到佢老婆仔女比人打果時有冇反應呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d124bf22777794edb444487b5f321b6a8f5bd842","tid":1355641,"uid":24477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c15f61cea4be09cda17b795f5e13acb2d83f